INSERT INTO `svr_content_pages` (`cnt_id`, `cnt_page`, `cnt_content`, `cnt_meta_title`, `cnt_meta_description`, `cnt_meta_keywords`, `cnt_status`, `cnt_orderby`, `cnt_dateadded`) VALUES (1,'About us','<p>\r\n	I extend My Hearty Greeting and Whole heartedly Welcome to you, your family, relatives and friends to <strong>SVR TRAVELS INDIA PVT LTD.</strong> SVR TRAVELS is the One Stop Solutions for all Travel needs for Everyone Offering starting from Tour Planning, Ticket Booking (Bus/Train/Flight/Ship),Providing Accommodation (Hotel/Resorts),Transportation (Car/Mini Bus/Bus)..etc end to end Services. SVR TRAVELS is serving in the Industry for the last 10 years and overcome the many Operational Issues and Become Perfect. SVR TRAVELS went on to pioneer the entire Offline and Online travel industry in India. SVR TRAVELS is the Leader of India&rsquo;s Offline/Online Travel.</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<u>http://www.svrtravelsindia.com</u> is India&rsquo;s leading Offline and Online travel company was founded in the year 2004 by Mr.S.Janardhan Reddy. Created to empower the Indian traveller with instant booking and comprehensive choices, the company began its journey in the India travel market. It aimed to offer a range of best-value products and services along with cutting-edge technology and dedicated round-the-clock customer support.</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	After consolidating its position in the market as a brand recognized for its reliability and transparency, SVR TRAVELS followed its success in the launching its online operations in 2014.</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	SVR TRAVELS&rsquo;s rise has been lead by the vision and the spirit of each one of its employees, for whom no idea was too big and no problem too difficult. With untiring innovation and determination, SVR TRAVELS proactively began to diversify its product offering, adding a variety of online and offline products and services. SVR TRAVELS also stayed ahead of the curve by continually evolving its technology to meet the ever changing demands of the rapidly developing global travel market.</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	Steadily establishing itself across India and the world, SVR TRAVELS simultaneously nurtured the growth of its offline businesses like its franchises and affiliates simultaneously, augmenting the brand&rsquo;s already strong retail presence further.</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	Today, SVR TRAVELS is much more than just a travel portal or a famous pioneering brand - it is a one-stop-travel-shop that offers the broadest selection of travel products and services in India. SVR TRAVELS is the dominant market-leader, a fact evinced by the trust placed in it by millions of happy customers.</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	Remaining reliable, efficient and at the forefront of technology, SVR TRAVELS&rsquo;s commitment and customer-centricity allows it to better understand and provide for its customers&rsquo; diverse needs and wants, and deliver consistently. With dedicated 24x7 customer support, SVR TRAVELS is there for you, whenever and wherever.</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<strong>SVR TRAVELS&rsquo;S SERVICES:</strong></p>\r\n<p>\r\n	&nbsp; Group/Individual Tourism Packages International and Domestic</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	&nbsp;Fixed Departure Tours</p>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp; Holiday Packages&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp; Students Educational Tours</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp; Honeymoon Tours</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp; Tailor-made Tour Packages</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp; International and Domestic Air Tickets</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp; LTC/LFC Tours</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp; Domestic Bus Tickets</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp; Private Car, Bus and Taxi Rentals</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp; VISA Assistance (Travel and Business)</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp; Hotel Bookings all Over India and World Wide</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp; B2B and Affiliate Services</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp; Certificate Attestation Services</div>\r\n<p style=\\\"\\\\&quot;\\\\\\\\&quot;\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\&quot;margin-left:-6.75pt;\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\&quot;\\\\\\\\&quot;\\\\&quot;\\\">\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div>\r\n	<p style