s - a rural, riverine expanse of verdant coconut groves and rice paddies. Overnight onboard Houseboat.\r\n','houseboat1534612264.jpg','Today you will board a Kettuvalam the famous Houseboats of Kerala. Cruise through the unique web of lakes, lagoons, canals, rivers and India&#39;s most enchanting areas - a rural, riverine expanse of verdant coconut groves and rice paddies. Overnight onboard Houseboat.\r\n','',1,'2017-08-17 16:13:44'),(603,14,'Day 05: Allepphy - Depart to Kochi Airport/rly stn','kochi airport1534612604.jpg','This Day After Breakfast Disembark from Cruise, you will Depart to Kochi Airport/rly stn for Back to Home ','kochi airport1534612604.jpg','This Day After Breakfast Disembark from Cruise, you will Depart to Kochi Airport/rly stn for Back to Home ','',1,'2017-08-17 16:16:08'),(604,117,'Day 01: Arrive Hyderabad','hyderabad1535605729.jpg','On Arrival at Hyderabad Airport/ Rly stn meet and Greet transfer to Hotel, Later Lunch you will proceed for visit to  Snow World, Birla Temple, Science Museum    in the Evening Free for Leisure Optional Explore to Surrounding Necklace road, Lumbini Park, NTR Garden Back to Hotel After Dinner Overnight at Hotel.','hyderabad1535605729.jpg','On Arrival at Hyderabad Airport/ Rly stn meet and Greet transfer to Hotel, Later Lunch you will proceed for visit to  Snow World, Birla Temple, Science Museum    in the Evening Free for Leisure Optional Explore to Surrounding Necklace road, Lumbini Park, NTR Garden Back to Hotel After Dinner Overnight at Hotel.','',1,'2017-08-18 22:03:10'),(605,117,'Day 02: Hyderabad','','This Day  After Breakfast  you will be proceed  to Sightseeing of Hyderabad    charminar icon of Hyderabad Built by Quli Qutub shah in 1591  Also visit to Adjusted  Mecca Masjid, Salarjung Museum is an art museum,   Later Lunch Proceed to   Golconda Fort  is a citadel and fort in Southern India and was the capital of the medieval sultanate of the Qutb Shahi dynasty  from 151 to 1687 Back to Hotel After Dinner  Overnight at Hotel.                                                      ','','','',1,'2017-08-18 22:03:47'),(606,117,'Day 03 : Hyderabad  - Srisailam(240 km/4-5 Hrs One Way)','','This Day Early Morning start to  Onward Journey  to Srisailam (Breakfast En-route) The Holy pilgrimage of Lord Mallikarjuna Temple(one of the 12 Jyothirlingas) in the Bank of River Krishna. En-route visit to Srisailam Dam  Arrive Check in to Hotel/Guest House  Overnight at  Hotel/Guest House.','','','',1,'2017-08-18 22:04:39'),(607,117,'Day 04 : Srisailam-Hyderabad(240 km/4-5 Hrs One Way)','','This Day Early Hours Proceed for Pooja and Dharshan of Lord Mallikarjuna Swamy Temple, Also visit to Papanashanam, While Back visit to Paladara and Panchdara  Start 05:00 Pm Back to Hyderabad, Overnight at Hyderabad Hotel.','','','',1,'2017-08-18 22:05:47'),(608,117,'Day 05 : Hyderabad - Ramoji Film city - Hyderabad','','This Day After Breakfast proceed to Full Day Ramoji film city famous for where you will be find live shooting&#39;s both bolly wood  and toly wood,  Explore and Enjoy with Live Shows and stunts shows in the Evening Back to Hotel Overnight at Hotel.','','','',1,'2017-08-18 22:06:29'),(609,117,'Day 06 : Depart to Hyderabad','','This Day After Breakfast you will Depart to Hyderabad Rly stn/Airport for Back to Home.','','','',1,'2017-08-18 22:07:05'),(610,36,'Day01: Departure from Hyderabad By Volvo','','Catch in the Evening Volvo Coach for onward journey Pune. Overnight at Volvo Coach','','','',1,'2017-09-01 22:18:10'),(611,118,'Day 1 :-  Arrival Bhubaneswar - Puri','','Pick Up From Bhuabaneswar Airport. EnroutVisit Dhauli ( the peace pagoda ).108 Shivling Templs, Lingra Temple.After Visit ForKonark for a visit to Sun Temple Pagoda at Konark (The Sun Temple), Chandrabhaga Beach & Ramchandi Temple. Aftert reach at Puri. Overnight at puri','','','',1,'2017-09-02 17:32:47'),(612,118,'Day 2:- Puri (Jagannath Templr) - Satpara/Chillika Lake','','After Morning breakfast.Visit for Darshan at Sri Jagannath Temple, Gundicha Temple. AfterDepart For Satpara, Chillika. The Fancy Land Of Irwadi Dolphins. Entire Day Sightseeing Of Satpara. Evening Return To Puri, Enjoy At Puri Beach.Overnight at Puri.','','','',1,'2017-09-02 17:33:57'),(613,118,'Day 3:- Puri - Konark - Bhubaneswar - Bhubaneswar Departure','','After Morning Breakfast Check Out From After reach at bhubaneswar. Localsightseeing of tribal museum , Khandagiri & Udaigiri Jain caves ( oldest rock cut caves, the caves arijjre reminiscent of influence of Buddhism and Jainism in Odisha (Orissa). At eveningDroop At Bhubaneswar Railway Station departure for Kolkata.','','','',1,'2017-09-02 17:35:09'),(614,118,'Day 4:-  Arrival Kolkata','','In the morning Pick Up From Kolkata Railway Station. After Check in Hotel. visit town trip covering Howrah Bridge*, Belur Math, Vivekananda Setu*, Dakshineswar Temple. Overnight stay at Hotel in Kolkata.','','','',1,'2017-09-02 17:35:43'),(615,118,'Day 5:-  Kolkata - Gangasagar - Kolkata','','After Breack fast full day excursion to Gangasagar - An island in the confluence of river Ganga & embayment of Bengal & well known for Kapil Muni Ashram which is advised to be a great devout significance. After back to Kolkata, Overnight in kolkata.','','','',1,'2017-09-02 17:36:24'),(616,118,'Day 6: Kolkata Local - Departure','','After Morning Breakfast. Visit To GPO*, Writers Building*, Eden flower bed Stadium*, St. Pauls Cathedral place of worship, Victoria Memorial auditorium, Drive Kali mander And more temples. Mother dwelling & Birla Mother dwelling & Birla Temple. Overnight stay at Kolkata. (*Drive Pass).After At evening Droop At Kolkata Airport. Happy Ending Journey With Sweet Memories.','','','',1,'2017-09-02 17:37:01'),(617,119,'DAY 01 On to Auckland - The city of Sails. Enjoy a birds eye view of Auckland city from the Skyci.','resize1514375576.jpg','On arrival at Auckland airport, you will be greeted by your friendly and experienced  Tour Manager / Local representative outs