 Base City of Maa Viashnodevi Temple Cehck in to Hotel After Fresh up Start trekking/By Pouni/By Heli  to Pooja and Dharshan Maa Vashnodevi Temple Back to Hotel Overnight at Hotel.\r\n','','','109376',1,'2014-09-14 20:15:16'),(127,27,'Day 2   :  Katra- Deaprt to Katra','day21410705951.jpg','This Day After Breakfast you will be Free for Leisure Optional you may visit to Shiva Khori Temple(80 km from Katra)  on your Own in the Evening we will Depart Katra for Back to Home\r\n','','','778514',1,'2014-09-14 20:15:51'),(128,28,'Day 01 : Hyderabad-Srisailam(240 km/4-5 Hrs One Way)','Day1_at_SrisailamDam1410706117.jpg','This  Day Early Hours Catch Bus06:00 Am Onward Journey  to Srisailam The Holy pilgrimage of Lord Mallikarjuna Temple(one of the 12 Jyothirlingas) in the Bank of River Krishna. En-route visit to Srisailam Dam  Arrive Check in to Guest House Overnight at Guest House.\r\n','','','577024',1,'2014-09-14 20:18:37'),(129,28,'Day 02 : Srisailam-Hyderabad(240 km/4-5 Hrs One Way)','Day2_at_temple1410706155.jpg','This Day Early Hours Proceed for Pooja and Dharshan of Lord Mallikarjuna Swamy Temple, Also visit to Papanashanam, While Back visit to Paladara and Panchdara  Start 05:00 Pm Back to Hyderabad\r\n','','','451084',1,'2014-09-14 20:19:15'),(130,29,'Day 01 : Arrive Visakhapatnam ','Day1_at_simhachalam-temple1410716139.jpg','Arrive Visakhapatnam meet & greet and transfer to hotel. Afternoon visit   Simhachalam (famous Vishnu Temple), Kailasagiri, Thotlakonda, boating at Fishing Harbour, Rushikonda Beach. Overnight  Stay at Vizag.\r\n','','','869547',1,'2014-09-14 23:05:39'),(131,29,'Day 02 : Vizag -Borra Caves- Araku Valley ','Day2_at_Borra-Caves1410716185.jpg','Morning proceed to Araku Valley same day return tour covering Padmapuram Gardens, Tribal Museum, Ananthagiri Coffee plantations, Galikonda view Point, Borra Caves. Overnight Stay  at  Aruk Valley .\r\n','','','175847',1,'2014-09-14 23:06:25'),(132,29,'Day 03 :Aruk Valley- Visakhapatnam ','Day3_at_Araku1410